    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一名调查员在神秘的档案室解密各种未知事件。作为团队创作的首款游戏，受到恐怖游戏独立制作人的感召，其灵感来源于都市怪谈与H.P.洛夫克拉夫特。致敬伟大的恐怖艺术！希望大家享受这趟奇异的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，切记保持身心健康。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在《H•P超自然事件档案》中，玩家可以….</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪️ 拨开层层迷雾，收集重要线索，调查超自然事件背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪️ 遭遇各种不可名状物，与之进行生死博弈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪️ 解锁特别行动档案，体验更多不同玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/873304ba53f9c1d7e244776bc76cd4da.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=146 /></span>▪️ 每个调查员都有属于自己的独特故事背景和职业特性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪️ 成长点数的分配和不同特性的构建将会为调查过程带来不一样的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/e8e79890203a7db6f0902c3a9eab819c.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=298 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/541bab11974ffc8d9db8b8b7252dc0e2.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=146 /></span>▪️ 在诡异的事件中保持理智，谨慎选择行动方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪️ 合理的选择能获取更多线索，让调查过程变得高效顺利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/c6808c1c1c6b6b6c331dcfc0609b53b4.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/4351ef238ffd290695920f0c47914ab0.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=146 /></span>▪️ 每个章节的调查过程中都会遭遇各种超自然生物的袭击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪️ 获得强力装备，灵活搭配武器技能可以更轻松地击败它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/89042902966ff6241cd1308770ba59d7.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=298 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/4048ae2109ba73616f0de7dc715026b8.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=146 /></span>▪️ 每个主线事件都拥有不同的结局，而支线任务的完成度将会影响结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪️ 所有事件调查完成后，特别行动档案将会全面开放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139670/extras/b3de440e47f4b4aa0e2bc51681347bec.avif?t=1753773306\" width=620 height=470 /></span></p>",
